onWebhookRequest(BotWebhookEvent) - Method in interface me.hopedev.topggwebhooks.bots.BotWebhookListener
Default implementation for listening to webhooks.
Code example:
public void onWebhookRequest(BotWebhookEvent event) {
System.out.println(event.isAuthorized() ? "Is authorized" : "is not authorized");

BotVoteData data = event.getVote();

System.out.println("botID: " + data.getBotID()); // 12345
System.out.println("UserID: " + data.getUserID()); // 12345
System.out.println("type: " + data.getType().name()); // UPVOTE
System.out.println("Weekend: " + data.isWeekend()); // true


}
onWebhookRequest(GuildWebhookEvent) - Method in interface me.hopedev.topggwebhooks.servers.GuildWebhookListener
Default implementation for listening to webhooks.
Code example:
public void onWebhookRequest(GuildWebhookEvent event) {
System.out.println(event.isValid() ? "valid" : "Not valid");
System.out.println(event.isAuthorized() ? "Is authorized" : "is not authorized");

GuildVoteData data = event.getVote();
System.out.println("GuildID: " + data.getGuildID()); // 12345
System.out.println("UserID: " + data.getUserID()); // 12345
System.out.println("type: " + data.getType().name()); // UPVOTEx


}
